	   <tr><td colspan=2>Damn when did bards get such an attitude wow. That sure seemed rude the wizard just said you need a group to get it and the bard went ape@#%^. Now my 2cents worth on getting it. 49ranger I was killing some of the gobbies for exp Light blue still exp and not to hard to kill when i got the helm. So decided to go find out about it. the lambent stone is easy just kill a SG if u can and if u can't check the merchants in the surrounding area around Oasis and Ro zones should find one there pretty easy for 20-40pp next u need to get the rune from Cazic not easy if u don't have some sort of invis and can get them alone with no healer types near. Found mine in the wrap around passage in the Throne room area. U can buy the 2 star rubies off of vendors or Players. The high lvl mob's in Seb and KC drop that quality of gems. Well off to go turn my stuff in and get a shiny blue helm.<br><br>Mystkyller Wyndryder Bertox server<br>&nbsp;<br>Mystkyller Wyndryder on Bertoxollous Server</td></tr>
